## SETUP INSTRUCTIONS

**Backend:**
```bash
cd nodeapp
npm install
npm start
```

**Frontend:**
```bash
cd react-app
npm install
npm start
```

**MongoDB:** Must be running on localhost:27017

Application runs on http://localhost:3000
